{"tid":593052,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖一定要驚喜？","createTime":"2018-03-14T16:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T05:06:10.000Z","uid":30076,"like":94,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"51d58d1a6d17300bd18f181dc87c5b926225a4e9","tid":593052,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"同另一半都拍咗拖4年喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過成日因爲節日呢d事鬧交<br />\n好似今日咁，無出街慶祝又嘈<br />\n但平時都見得幾密，一星期兩至三日，聖誕呀情人節都會出黎（2月14）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又成日叫我送禮物，當然佢唔係叫我送咩好貴嘅嘢。只係想我有份心意。但我唔明點解節日一定要出街，送禮物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想送嘅任何時候都可以送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我平時見到啱佢嘅嘢都會買比佢。<br />\n我係唔識比驚喜人嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，例如我買左份聖誕禮物/生日禮物我唔會當日送。因為我好心急見到對方收到我禮物個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好想佢快D用到。<br />\n仲有女朋友成日叫我送花。屌，我覺得好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又唔係平，又無用，做裝飾又好快淍。我寧願比多幾百買實用嘅嘢或者食餐好嘅。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪我呢個心態有問題，係咪我唔夠浪漫？到底應該係我去改變自己做一個有驚喜嘅人，定係等佢接受我係一個不浪漫嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n可能我1999，當比個地方我呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c43c4d88b03052e3078a1f559500ebdf1a3663c","tid":593052,"uid":16425,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"女人係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3678716a65f4d4de6434f60d8368be07dab49f26","tid":593052,"uid":170867,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"價值觀唔同都拍到4年 西利"},{"pid":"6e943b2fdbc55c13c13772bacece3e3f6893150d","tid":593052,"uid":30076,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3678716a65f4d4de6434f60d8368be07dab49f26","tid":593052,"uid":170867,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"價值觀唔同都拍到4年 西利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"係，可能大家當初都以對方為終生伴侶<br />\n每次有問題都會傾"},{"pid":"eb3e21311409b0d41ed78c703083be2d266f0953","tid":593052,"uid":106375,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"佢都開到聲叫你送花已經算好<br />\n有啲唔講自己想要咩但又想要有驚喜先煩"},{"pid":"3b35884c959320c06a23bbf9f9ed89c79dee96bd","tid":593052,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"另一半係獨立tpye 對節日同一般般 驚喜就可有可無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a45892025f246c1bad77ef035b52baf339dbfe","tid":593052,"uid":157063,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"買花真係最撚on9 既事<br />\n拎黎post ig fb同埋行街有得拎住黎曬命"},{"pid":"94efb48e7ee43d2e5e9ed93595f5e8532bff9af4","tid":593052,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"價值觀唔同"},{"pid":"5a2189a77adb6b2f99a2de9b0d2b077cf4b57eab","tid":593052,"uid":147532,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"一齊四年，都要D新鮮感嘅，況且禮物唔一定要洗錢，佢中意花，你可以試下整紙摺花/畫花/朱古力花比佢，又唔洗錢又有誠意。"},{"pid":"3afb7167788a1d0d534af71cc2e25866b29a2a79","tid":593052,"uid":69614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:11:34.000Z","msg":"咁生日紀念日送吓花都可以<br />\n節日就唔好啦"},{"pid":"66d7351e8e2885ddfdece8009c7ca420fa4b7612","tid":593052,"uid":30076,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3afb7167788a1d0d534af71cc2e25866b29a2a79","tid":593052,"uid":69614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:11:34.000Z","msg":"咁生日紀念日送吓花都可以<br />\n節日就唔好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"過唔到自己嗰關，好撚浪費"},{"pid":"390f0090cabe884ddc3f3502d3e96c4acd1887ae","tid":593052,"uid":30076,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"5a2189a77adb6b2f99a2de9b0d2b077cf4b57eab","tid":593052,"uid":147532,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"一齊