01.000Z","msg":"我同另一半平時都會送小禮物/見到啱對方嘅野，同埋會留意下對方有咩想要/有咩需要，我仲會記錄喺電話度，臨近大時大節就plan定買咩，會買定先，收埋喺櫃桶，等正日再送比對方，見到對方又驚又喜就好開心<br />\n<br />\n每人拍拖方式唔同嘅，要磨合同互相遷就。你唔like驚喜嘅，女友都要明白，唔能夠次次都要求有驚喜。相反，你女友like驚喜嘅，你咪就下佢，偶爾都plan下驚喜囉～"},{"pid":"2b2bf02a4dde02250249c0155879e09c0c94a070","tid":593052,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a19e43a0b756bf537383709d72f74b93d57df329","tid":593052,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75d99e3e96f01e857467bd4c343f71e105832c1","tid":593052,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14631a068d4b2fd7e13197a5fe86ae0b85946980","tid":593052,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"見過有啲男仔送完花俾女仔, 影完張相之後, 係個男仔拎返住紥花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"都唔輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有d送大大集公仔，影完相曬命之後屋企無位放，又塞比男友帶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:22:56.000Z","msg":"何苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"所以送一枝岩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dbf7b2a073e9038702ad2758c93fb4b847eb75","tid":593052,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"637c86c8da6d721275f40ecece793d6237fea631","tid":593052,"uid":83610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位嘅意見。黎緊試下送d亁花<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶有 又平又靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"有無非淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."}]}